# SEO & Content System

## Every new page
- Unique `<title>` + meta description
- Canonical `https://eillon.maison/...`
- hreflang where applicable (see index.html pattern)
- Run `npm run build:sitemap` if new route

## Structured data
Valid JSON-LD; match patterns on beles.html / journal articles.

## Internal linking
Funnel: journal/education → `/beles` → `#waitlist`. Use descriptive anchor text, not "click here".

## Voice
SEO clarity without generic "best perfume" listicle tone. See `DESIGN.md`.

## Verify
`npm run verify:links` after link changes.
